						<p>Thanks. Glad you liked it &#8211; the vibe you got is very much what I was trying to achieve. I&#8217;m pretty happy with protagonists, as I see the characters as the leads in the story around this micfic. But, I agree about the bits around the speech. I am beginning to try my hand at that and still finding my way. I wasn&#8217;t entirely happy with Going, going, gone and your version definitely reads better.</p>
