						<p>Thanks for the lovely comments <span class='wp-smiley wp-emoji wp-emoji-smile' title=':-)'>:-)</span> </p>
<p>It is interesting how people view what one has written in different ways &#8211; that is one of the fascinating things about this micfic exercise. For example, I didn&#8217;t see the auction as low-brow, just rural, small town and somewhat in the past. But I like that you could read it quite differently and still enjoy it and find it reasonably consistent.</p>
